{"tid":128343,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"如果夜神月寫呢啲野落去","createTime":"2017-02-20T17:19:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T10:56:38.000Z","uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b7088d10327f7e92ce8768d4cdd012d2821453a4","tid":128343,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:19:12.000Z","msg":"先準備好一段文字，內容係寫上人嘅名<br />\n<br />\n1.先殺調查總部其中一個人，命令佢係 筆記1 寫上夜神月老豆同事嘅名<br />\n<br />\n2.準備好一個位置放上寫好文字嘅筆記， 筆記1 令呢個同事係準備好 筆記2 上寫名，一次寫晒全部同組調查成員嘅名<br />\n<br />\n3. 筆記2 發動，計好時間，全部人拎槍殺自稱L，有L特徵嘅人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁樣係咪一集就做完？"},{"pid":"8f19e4720fbd751f8ce35c5db5c5a275943010ec","tid":128343,"uid":63360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:19:37.000Z","msg":"未必"},{"pid":"a69d3481f07e7e09c25342887517cd2188c08e18","tid":128343,"uid":18200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:21:03.000Z","msg":"屌你重睇啦 規則都未撚熟"},{"pid":"f420d7b07d4d302b66fe4a73d4c20367ae0f5ebc","tid":128343,"uid":13543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:23:46.000Z","msg":"如果我冇記錯<br />\n咁會全部直接心臟麻痺"},{"pid":"7fb7904a6f2ba308da60de5fdaeb9e8ad5188966","tid":128343,"uid":36414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:23:58.000Z","msg":"死淨佢一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d54b86b4e394cb66db1bd8234ba9e68ad8245d0c","tid":128343,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:25:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果我冇記錯<br />\n咁會全部直接心臟麻痺</blockquote><br />\n寫得三個字都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"d1bd4dcd93d7fd91bbcafeaf7745451e5990ccc3","tid":128343,"uid":29790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:25:45.000Z","msg":"不如話佢肯換死神眼好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae4a1976fb42cc9add071e49c9c320208639d